Package gust.backend.transport

Interface TransportConfig

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    GoogleTransportConfig, GrpcTransportConfig, PooledTransportConfig
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FirestoreTransportConfig
    public interface TransportConfig
    Specifies base configuration properties generally supported by all transport configurations. This includes properties like keepalive timeouts and timings, pooling settings, and so on.
